attribution.changeMessage: Her death certificate states that she died 8 July 1853 at Albion Road in the sub-district of Woolwich Dockyard, district of Greenwich, Kent County.

The Union Chapel Register of Burials in Woolwich, Kent 1850-1854, found at Ancestry.com in the England & Wales, Non-Conformist and Non-Parochial Registers, 1567-1970, show that Margret Griffith was buried 11 July 1853.
